      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must belong to a Scheduled Caste (SC) community.\n1. The applicant must be part of an Antyodaya (AAY) family.\n1. The applicant’s annual family income should not exceed ₹3,00,000/-.\n1. The applicant must be a resident of Gujarat.\n1. The applicant should be a self-help group of unemployed persons. \n1. The applicant must be a member of a registered self-help group (SHG) or apply individually with valid business intent.\n\n<br>\n\n",
